metadata.name: stETH Leverage
metadata.description: This vault leverages stETH yield by depositing stETH into Morpho - borrowing wETH and stake it for more stETH, which is then deposited again into Morpho. This is achieved via flash loans in order to reach the desired leverage in one transaction
